          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2087.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of vegetable oil if it's looking a little dry</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>rosemary sprigs</strong>, <strong>drained potatoes </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook, stirring frequently, for 15-17 min or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>sautéed potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2087.-step-5-x200.jpg",
